name: Tainakel
description:
Instructions

Arrows/WASD to move (you can also tap on the sides of the screen

Z to undo

R to reset

< to move back a level, > to move forwards a level (i.e. if you are stuck)

Description

Snake-o-ban style game where you try to drop a trophy in a hole underground. I mean, all these trophies you trying to find in thousands of different RPGs have got to be placed there somehow!
